<div class="min-h-screen px-6 sm:px-20 py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-center mb-2">About DayTrip</h1>
  <p class="text-center text-base-content/60 mb-12">Built by one person. Because I-70 on a powder day is a nightmare alone.</p>

  <%# Origin story %>
  <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md mb-10">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-2">The Story</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
        Hey, I'm Tyler. Every ski season I'd watch people sitting alone bumper to bumper on I-70 and think there had to be a better way to do this.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        If you're already driving up to Breckenridge or Vail, why not bring someone along and split the cost? And if you don't have a car, why miss out when someone's already heading that direction?
      </p>
      <p class="text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        Works for hikes, lakes, day trips too. Basically anywhere worth the drive is worth sharing a ride.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Values %>
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What I care about</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
          <div class="bg-accent/10 rounded-full p-4 mb-2">
            <%= lucide_icon('mountain', class: 'text-accent w-8 h-8') %>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Getting Outside</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Missing a powder day because you don't have a car is the worst. DayTrip makes it easier to find a seat when you need one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
          <div class="bg-accent/10 rounded-full p-4 mb-2">
            <%= lucide_icon('heart-handshake', class: 'text-accent w-8 h-8') %>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Actual Trust</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">Driver profiles, real photos, and honest reviews so you know who you're getting in the car with before you commit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
        <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
          <div class="bg-accent/10 rounded-full p-4 mb-2">
            <%= lucide_icon('leaf', class: 'text-accent w-8 h-8') %>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Fewer Empty Seats</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70">I-70 is bad enough as it is. One less solo driver means one less car in that mess and one more person having a good day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Contact %>
  <div class="card bg-primary text-primary-content shadow-md mb-10">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-2">Say hi ðŸ‘‹</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90">
        This is a side project and I'm always improving it. If something's broken, confusing, or you have an idea, shoot me an email. I actually read them.
      </p>
      <div class="card-actions mt-4 flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="mailto:support@daytrip.com" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm text-primary-content border-primary-content hover:bg-primary-content hover:text-primary">
          <%= lucide_icon('mail', class: 'w-4 h-4') %>
          Email me
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/tylerriehl" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm text-primary-content border-primary-content hover:bg-primary-content hover:text-primary">
          <%= lucide_icon('coffee', class: 'w-4 h-4') %>
          Buy me a coffee
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# CTA %>
  <div class="text-center py-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
    <%= link_to 'Explore Rides', rides_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg' %>
    <%= link_to 'How It Works', how_it_works_path, class: 'btn btn-outline btn-lg' %>
  </div>
</div>
